							href="https://www.iso.org/standard/iso-iec-27000-family"
							rel="external"
							title="International Organization for Standardization ISO/IEC 27000 family"
							>ISO27K</a
						> standards. Ensure compliance and protection for your digital assets.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<img
						alt=""
						height="3500"
						src="/images/training.jpg"
						width="2333"
					/>
					<h3>Training</h3>
					<p>
						Boost cyber defense with tailored awareness campaigns, relevant
						newsletters, tabletop drills, and incident response workshops.
						Strengthen your team today.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div class="why">
			<heading>
