		class="about"
	>
		<header>
			<h2>About CyberFern</h2>
		</header>
		<div>
			<div class="about-content">
				<p>CyberFern was founded by Anna Lezhikova.</p>
				<p>
					She has over 20 years of experience in communications, business
					management, software development, DevOps, and DevSecOps. She
					understands not only the technology, but also people and processes:
					the triad of good cybersecurity.
				</p>
				<p>
					Let&rsquo;s work together to protect what matters most to you and your
					organisation.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
